es\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"the LA Games\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"four years' time\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Next Olympics, he wants to compete for the Philippines,' Carrion said.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.780705032729806, \"rank\": 0.18146074692105835, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Next Olympics\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"Carrion\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So we will seek FIG's permission.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.466017049072243e-28, \"text\": \"FIG\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will write a letter and we will see if FIG says yes or no.'\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.466017049072243e-28, \"text\": \"FIG\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jarman was asked about Carrion's comments during an interview with members of the Philippine Olympic Committee media - as reported by GMA News Online - and the 22-year-old insisted he had no immediate plans to ditch Team GB.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.504171682269197e-19, \"text\": \"Carrion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrion\"}, {\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippine Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8876532648824914, \"rank\": 0.07347525962140282, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jarman\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"GMA News Online\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"no immediate plans\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Jarman said he could be open to the prospect in the latter years of his career should the rules allow it.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jarman\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter years\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me, competing for the Philippines, it would be amazing, but at the moment, it's hard for me to make a decision like that,' Jarman said.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.780705032729806, \"rank\": 0.18146074692105835, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"Jarman\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have got family back in the UK, but I think for me, if maybe I am in the end of my career, maybe I am still at peak performance, who knows, maybe?\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999926333908513, \"rank\": 6.977001707636097e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"peak performance\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I definitely would not be closing any doors but I think for the next four years, I will still be definitely with UK.'\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999926333908513, \"rank\": 6.977001707636097e-06, \"text\": \"UK\